{"tid":759991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「酒樓部長優先畀位，你送禮物答謝」，算唔算行賄？","createTime":"2018-07-29T06:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T15:27:12.000Z","uid":29314,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"aff8a83de2e80ea292240009ebd9d13700e8c565","tid":759991,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:48:38.000Z","msg":"有無專家答到？"},{"pid":"4f0eb8affd5a5de315431fe315b11456a1ce16ba","tid":759991,"uid":106929,"like":11,"dislike":10,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"酒樓 熟客好賺<br />\n<br />\n有d有米 訂台 買卷 好闊佬<br />\n<br />\n我係老細 都優待熟客仔"},{"pid":"7f150d11dc76090898011230f61b35a7e0b42d00","tid":759991,"uid":29314,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>酒樓 熟客好賺<br />\n<br />\n有d有米 訂台 買卷 好闊佬<br />\n<br />\n我係老細 都優待熟客仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公司授權你咁做就係。<br />\n<br />\n但如果無公司授權，而你私底下做，收取利益就唔係。"},{"pid":"f7885dda288047e26c9d66b034c37acdc1281533","tid":759991,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4df20da56b8a4ed425cc65a6b2629fc78e6d358f","tid":759991,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aeabd161405cdeb844cac9933ddbd06f2542649","tid":759991,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你隻乞衣狗仲未收皮嘅</blockquote><br />\n真乖，唔使叫都識入黎幫我推post"},{"pid":"a5d5f6c5aab661659970fb8baa4edb1d83132537","tid":759991,"uid":107212,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7885dda288047e26c9d66b034c37acdc1281533","tid":759991,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:58:33.000Z","msg":"你都未收啦"},{"pid":"8f9cd9d29351e7443ff5476d72e1e0ff0fda03cd","tid":759991,"uid":107212,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{